Rating: 3
Just made this dish for my partner. It was wonderful. Please take the time to make the candied butternut squash - not only is it delicious on its own, but it adds a wonderful, sweet moistness to the couscous. Thought it wouldn't be spicy enough, so I added the following amounts of spices in place of the cinnamon: 1 1/2 t. cumin, 1 1/2 t. sweet paprika, 1/2 t. of tumeric, 1/2 t. ground coriander, 1/8 t. cinnamon. Again, it was wonderful!

